data.description: SELLER PAID CLOSING COST! PRICED TO SELL! Buyer to receive $3,000 towards closing cost with an accepted offer by 12/22. This spacious modern gem, constructed in 2021, offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience on over 4 acres of beautiful land. This newly built home exudes modern elegance, with a stunning fireplace, a gourmet kitchen, open floorplan and even a garden sink, ensuring both style and functionality in every corner. Imagine chilly evenings by the fireplace, creating the perfect ambiance for relaxation and gatherings. With over 4 acres of land, the possibilities for outdoor activities and creating your own paradise are endless. Parking is ample, so there's no need to worry about where to park your vehicles. Don't let this rare opportunity slip away! Contact James at (864) 559-9896 or via email at Gethome@thejoshuaway.com to schedule a viewing. MOTIVATED SELLER.
